ors are affected by surface color and reflectivity — dark/black surfaces give weak returns","Add 10uF cap across VCC-GND close to sensor to reduce supply noise"],"datasheet_url":"https://global.sharp/products/device/lineup/data/pdf/datasheet/gp2y0a51sk_e.pdf"},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[[65,69],[75,79]]},